- New coverage_snapshots table stores full HTML in Neon DB
- /api/coverage-html serves latest DB snapshot (fallback: static file)
- /api/coverage/upload accepts an HTML file upload and saves to DB
- Coverage iframe now points to /api/coverage-html
- Upload page redesigned: Download button + 3-step flow + file drop zone
  + upload history table showing all previous uploads
- Migration: migrations/003_coverage_snapshots.sql (run in Neon console)

Co-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
